He
began
to
ransack
his
tutor's
desk
for
a
piece
of
wax
or
twine
necessary
to
his
work.
Moore
happened
to
be
absent.
Mr.
Hall,
indeed,
had
called
for
him
to
take
a
long
walk.
Henry
could
not
immediately
find
the
object
of
his
search.
He
rummaged
compartment
after
